channel.title: Frunescape source
channel.description:
Hey everyone i finnaly found out how to compile so i thought i might release my first source ever this is a good source its a port 43594 here is my source download
[url=http://uppit.com/R085RR]http://uppit.com/R085RR[/url]
Have fun with my source! I updated it so yea i added more commands ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~Feature's~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ *Brand new type of home first ever home like my home *churchpk *great vengance *added a command to make hiddenadmins ::givehadmin user *Cool command that make u look messed up ::mesedup ::messedup2 ::messedup3 ::unmessedup ::newpk ::church And many more good commands *cool area's ::staff ::ploiks ::gage ::hybrid j0e~ the source you downloaded the code is now ::wars *New kind of portals Got em to work and made them take you some place
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~Next source update's~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ *new commands like: ::jail user ::armour (this will give you random armour) maybe more i havent thought of any yet! *New area's like: *new pk place *new training place *npc updates *new npc's *new npc drops *new shops *new home (this means ima make diffrent walls and add a new room to it) *new skilling area's like they wont be cluttered in one area they will be spread out *new xp's ( source will be fast levling and another slow leveling)
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ well hope you like my source ty ploiks and please do not leech!!
Please give me credit!!

item.dc:creator: @klownsrus klownsrus
item.description:
@klownsrus wrote:

lol yes his source is plian, and im his brother and i used the same source he used to start out which was sunny- [something] but we have edited it alot, and i did take his idea on the home and i made the same type of portals and he copyed my on that but i only have one, and my source is in its snowing state.

well i will add pics soon but here are some info about the source that im going to release.

[ul][li]Way Better staff Area (Located at the entrance of shantys pass)[/li]
[li]More Custom Commands like ::church (to get your prayers up)[/li]
[li]New Traing area Comming Soon! (Old Frugooscape’s training area {when it first came out})[/li]
[li]Mods can use ::banuser but they cant unban[/li]
[li]Made staff more appricaited, so they can do some commands they never could have done before[/li]
[li]In the process of making secret places for staff(ill add pics later or tomorrow)[/li]
[li]Im making a new town from scratch by using a plan area (like the build center on frugooscape)[/li]
[li]Workin on custom items[/li]
[li]Made a good client, but im working on a client with a port changer besides just server ip {So runescape don’t sue me}[/li]
[li]working on buying a webdomain and working on a webclient that ill release for people to add on their sites[/li][/ul]
